{"tid":169583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為救行山休班警喪命 張曉明：港人要更尊重紀律部隊","createTime":"2017-03-24T09:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T14:31:44.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a195fb9784ae2583cbbe53fb2a2fa8e1571c9ec8","tid":169583,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170324/large/1490347196_989a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170324%2Flarge%2F1490347196_989a.jpg&h=98122312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防總隊目邱少明日前於馬鞍山吊手岩，拯救行山迷路的休班機場特警和保安時，墮崖殉職。多名市民及同袍，繼續前往邱少明生前駐守的田心消防局弔唁。中聯辦主任張曉明亦有到場，並向記者指，警方、消防等紀律部隊，為保障港人生命安全，可能要付出性命代價，呼籲港人對他們要有更多尊重和敬意。"},{"pid":"8bf68b52b002c0e193c1f4b29a8c387f9028527a","tid":169583,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"消防年年都死幾件 差佬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2f9a37c2bbda99b137f102205d51aaef203e54","tid":169583,"uid":33178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"係啊 但唔包黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機場特警都被困<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係好似連登仔咁講少於操練<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c056fbb3ace3bb84ad1a4f3a473b1cea25eec539","tid":169583,"uid":15739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"阿蛇行山洗你教"},{"pid":"80e5708387a4e644e7022671b2422b2ab7f1f221","tid":169583,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime